name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Dune Data Extractor by Table Capture

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Allows you to extract data from Dune queries view to Excel (XLSX) or CSV.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The Dune Data Extractor allows you to export query results to a CSV or Microsoft Excel file (or copy the data to the clipboard).

Features:
• Export to Microsoft Excel (XLSX), CSV
• Copy to Clipboard
• Break massive result sets into files with 10K rows each

How it works:
• Just right-click to download in your desired format
• You get 5 free exports, afterwards you can purchase a 25-pack of exports or a license for unlimited exports.

Updated: 12/5/2024
